      "text": [
        " اَلْمَسْجِدِ فَقَالَ «قُولُوا لَهُ لاَ رَدَّ اَللَّهُ عَلَيْكَ ضَالَّتَكَ فَإِنَّهَا لِغَيْرِ هَذَا بُنِيَتْ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.714 - The Prophet (sw), heard a man searching for a lost item in the mosque and said:\n\"Say to him, 'May Allah (swt) not return your lost item to you,' for the mosque was not built for this purpose.\""
        ]
      }
